# Project context (read this first)
This repo is a monorepo:
- `frontend/`: Vite + React + TypeScript, Ant Design, React Router, MobX State Tree, TanStack Query
- `backend/`: FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + Alembic + pipeline code
- Local infra: Postgres + MinIO via docker compose

# Non-negotiables
- Small diffs; avoid unrelated refactors.
- Don’t invent endpoints/schemas—inspect the repo and reuse existing patterns.
- Financial data is sensitive: do not log raw CSV rows or expose secrets.

# Verification (run after changes)
- Frontend: `cd frontend && npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm run build`
- Backend: `cd backend && ruff check . && ruff format --check . && pytest -q`
- If you changed DB schema: `cd backend && alembic upgrade head`
